<div class="container">
  <div class="jumbotron" id="title">
    <h1>Mabel's Mega Milkshakes</h1><br>
    <p>Welcome to Mable's, home of the mega milkshake. We start with simply decadent milkshakes, then pile on even more
      goodness. Simply scrumptious! We have listed our current and previous offerings. Did we miss your favorite
      milkshake? Add it to our list. Is our list outdated? Please move or delete a flavor. And most of all... enjoy!</p>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Current Offerings</h2><br>
        <ul>
          {{#each shakes}}
          {{#unless devoured}}
          {{> shakes/shake-block consumed=true}}
          {{/unless}}
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Blasts from the Past</h2><br>
        <ul>
          {{#each shakes}}
          {{#if devoured}}
          {{> shakes/shake-block consumed=false}}
          {{/if}}
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <form class="form">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="ca">Suggest a flavor!</label>
        <input type="text" id="newFlavor" name="name">
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="devoured">Is this suggestion for current or past offerings?</label>
        <input type="radio" name="devoured" value="1" checked>Current
        <input type="radio" name="devoured" value="0"> Past
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn" id="addShake">Add shake</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>